  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell (pre-Nymeria).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg/50px-House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg/75px-House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/be/House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg/100px-House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Morgan Martell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell (pre-Nymeria).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg/50px-House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/be/House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg/75px-House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/be/House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg/100px-House_Martell_%28pre-Nymeria%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Sandship\" title=\"Lord of the Sandship\">Lord of the Sandship</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Morgan Martell</b> was an <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> adventurer and the founder of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Morgan_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Morgan and his kin descended on lands loosely held by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wade\" title=\"House Wade\">House Wade</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Shell_(Dorne)\" title=\"House Shell (Dorne)\">House Shell</a>, defeated them in battle, seized their villages, burned their castles and established his dominion over a strip of coastland fifty leagues long and ten leagues wide.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_the_andals_arrive.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_the_andals_arrive.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Morgan_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></s